hw4: Projections in 3D

John Osborne
CSCI4229/5229 Fall 2019

Allow a scene to be naviageted in top down orthographic, top down perspective, and first person

Key bindings
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  In First Person -
 		W      Move forward
 		A      Move Backward
 		S      Strafe Left
 		D      Strafe Right
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

  To Run:
  "make" to build
  hw4.exe to run
